title: Radical Notions: Making Marriage and Motherhood Cool Again, a Call to Joy and Adventure, not The End
description:
What does it mean to approach personhood, marriage and motherhood through a lens of adventure and potential for joy? Karen talks to Stephanie about her journey through depression and anxiety, healing from anger and her choice to become a wife and mother. 
Were there sacrifices involved? What does it mean to grieve disappointments? What does it mean to become a whole person?

Resources mentioned by Stephanie:

Her Youtube Channel:  Happier on a Horse
https://youtu.be/BTDbiwJv4uk

The Five Love Languages: the Secret to Love that Lasts
by Gary Chapman

The Meaning Code Conversation with Fr. Jon Beadle about Harry Potter:
https://youtu.be/3OSOULhXRIo

Books by Brennan Manning:
Abba's Child, the Cry of the Heart for Intimate Belonging
The Ragamuffin Gospel

Books by Johann Hair
Lost Connections (about Depression and Anxiety)
Stolen Focus (about the dangers of online addiction)
